Heat oven to 425 degrees F. Place all ingredients on 15x10 baking pan with sides. Toss to coat with the oil. Season lightly with salt and pepper. Cover pan tightly with foil. Roast 30 minutes. Remove foil and stir; roast an additional 30 minutes or until bratwurst are hot and vegetables are tender. Enjoy with your favorite Archer Farms mustard on the side.